{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":133,"text":"I'm a teacher and a practitioner"},{"time":2014,"text":"of civics in America."},{"time":4499,"text":"Now, I will kindly ask those of\nyou who have just fallen asleep"},{"time":7571,"text":"to please wake up. (Laughter)"},{"time":9683,"text":"Why is it that the very word \"civics\""},{"time":11974,"text":"has such a soporific, \neven a narcoleptic effect"},{"time":14865,"text":"on us?"},{"time":16171,"text":"I think it's because the very \nword signifies something"},{"time":20312,"text":"exceedingly virtuous, \nexceedingly important,"},{"time":23420,"text":"and exceedingly boring."},{"time":25830,"text":"Well, I think it's the responsibility of people like us,"},{"time":28883,"text":"people who show up for gatherings like this"},{"time":30637,"text":"in person or online, in any way we can,"},{"time":33384,"text":"to make civics sexy again,"},{"time":36285,"text":"as sexy as it was during the American Revolution,"},{"time":39111,"text":"as sexy as it was during the Civil Rights Movement."},{"time":42554,"text":"And I believe the way we make civics sexy again"},{"time":45760,"text":"is to make explicitly about the teaching of power."},{"time":50110,"text":"The way we do that, I believe,"},{"time":52603,"text":"is at the level of the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54997,"text":"This is what I want to talk about today,"},{"time":56796,"text":"and I want to start by defining some terms"},{"time":59108,"text":"and then I want to describe the scale"},{"time":61183,"text":"of the problem I think we face"},{"time":63046,"text":"and then suggest the ways that I believe cities"},{"time":65472,"text":"can be the seat of the solution."},{"time":67992,"text":"So let me start with some definitions."},{"time":71780,"text":"By civics, I simply mean the art"},{"time":73557,"text":"of being a pro-social, problem-solving contributor"},{"time":76808,"text":"in a self-governing community."},{"time":78935,"text":"Civics is the art of citizenship,"},{"time":81364,"text":"what Bill Gates Sr. calls simply"},{"time":83479,"text":"showing up for life,"},{"time":85571,"text":"and it encompasses three things:"},{"time":87956,"text":"a foundation of values,"},{"time":91500,"text":"an understanding of the systems\nthat make the world go round,"},{"time":95266,"text":"and a set of skills"},{"time":97620,"text":"that allow you to pursue goals"},{"time":99104,"text":"and to have others join in that pursuit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102777,"text":"And that brings me to my definition of power,"},{"time":105036,"text":"which is simply this:"},{"time":107204,"text":"the capacity to make others do"},{"time":109870,"text":"what you would have them do."},{"time":112631,"text":"It sounds menacing, doesn't it?"},{"time":115312,"text":"We don't like to talk about power."},{"time":117653,"text":"We find it scary. We find it somehow evil."},{"time":123347,"text":"We feel uncomfortable naming it."},{"time":125129,"text":"In the culture and mythology of democracy,"},{"time":127542,"text":"power resides with the people."},{"time":129285,"text":"Period. End of story."},{"time":131078,"text":"Any further inquiry not necessary"},{"time":132653,"text":"and not really that welcome."},{"time":134633,"text":"Power has a negative moral valence."},{"time":138691,"text":"It sounds Machiavellian inherently."},{"time":141473,"text":"It seems inherently evil."},{"time":144107,"text":"But in fact power is no more inherently good or evil"},{"time":147912,"text":"than fire or physics."},{"time":151030,"text":"It just is."},{"time":153140,"text":"And power governs"},{"time":154346,"text":"how any form of government operates,"},{"time":155947,"text":"whether a democracy or a dictatorship."},{"time":159427,"text":"And the problem we face today,\nhere in America in particular,"},{"time":162668,"text":"but all around the world,"},{"time":164198,"text":"is that far too many people \nare profoundly illiterate"},{"time":167483,"text":"in power â€”"},{"time":169463,"text":"what it is, who has it,"},{"time":171533,"text":"how it operates, how it flows,"},{"time":173996,"text":"what part of it is visible, \nwhat part of it is not,"},{"time":176516,"text":"why some people have it, \nwhy that's compounded."},{"time":180128,"text":"And as a result of this illiteracy,"},{"time":183617,"text":"those few who do understand"},{"time":186483,"text":"how power operates in civic life,"},{"time":188973,"text":"those who understand"},{"time":190311,"text":"how a bill becomes a law, yes,"},{"time":192134,"text":"but also how a friendship \nbecomes a subsidy,"},{"time":196289,"text":"or how a bias becomes a policy,"},{"time":199694,"text":"or how a slogan becomes a movement,"},{"time":202629,"text":"the people who understand those things"},{"time":204609,"text":"wield disproportionate influence,"},{"time":206180,"text":"and they're perfectly happy"},{"time":207660,"text":"to fill the vacuum created by the ignorance"},{"time":210740,"text":"of the great majority."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215124,"text":"This is why it is so fundamental for us right now"},{"time":218543,"text":"to grab hold of this idea of power"},{"time":222999,"text":"and to democratize it."},{"time":224755,"text":"One of the things that is so profoundly exciting"},{"time":229299,"text":"and challenging about this moment"},{"time":231282,"text":"is that as a result of this power illiteracy"},{"time":234484,"text":"that is so pervasive,"},{"time":237151,"text":"there is a concentration"},{"time":240240,"text":"of knowledge, of understanding, of clout."},{"time":244491,"text":"I mean, think about it:"},{"time":246578,"text":"How does a friendship become a subsidy?"},{"time":249993,"text":"Seamlessly,"},{"time":251270,"text":"when a senior government official decides"},{"time":253905,"text":"to leave government and become a lobbyist"},{"time":256402,"text":"for a private interest"},{"time":258316,"text":"and convert his or her relationships into capital"},{"time":261018,"text":"for their new masters."},{"time":263325,"text":"How does a bias become a policy?"},{"time":265750,"text":"Insidiously, just the way that"},{"time":269350,"text":"stop-and-frisk, for instance,"},{"time":271510,"text":"became over time a bureaucratic numbers game."},{"time":275166,"text":"How does a slogan become a movement?"},{"time":278271,"text":"Virally, in the way that the Tea Party, for instance,"},{"time":281252,"text":"was able to take the \"Don't Tread on Me\" flag"},{"time":284718,"text":"from the American Revolution,"},{"time":286465,"text":"or how, on the other side,"},{"time":288315,"text":"a band of activists could take a magazine headline,"},{"time":291279,"text":"\"Occupy Wall Street,\""},{"time":293216,"text":"and turn that into a global meme and movement."},{"time":296132,"text":"The thing is, though, most people"},{"time":298638,"text":"aren't looking for and don't\nwant to see these realities."},{"time":301890,"text":"So much of this ignorance, this civic illiteracy,"},{"time":305325,"text":"is willful."},{"time":307122,"text":"There are some millennials, for instance,"},{"time":308970,"text":"who think the whole business is just sordid."},{"time":311636,"text":"They don't want to have anything to do with politics."},{"time":313312,"text":"They'd rather just opt out"},{"time":314391,"text":"and engage in volunteerism."},{"time":317179,"text":"There are some techies out there"},{"time":319372,"text":"who believe that the cure-all"},{"time":320668,"text":"for any power imbalance or power abuse"},{"time":323216,"text":"is simply more data,"},{"time":325610,"text":"more transparency."},{"time":328093,"text":"There are some on the left who think power resides"},{"time":330308,"text":"only with corporations,"},{"time":332167,"text":"and some on the right who think power"},{"time":334090,"text":"resides only with government,"},{"time":335603,"text":"each side blinded by their selective outrage."},{"time":339964,"text":"There are the naive who believe that"},{"time":342008,"text":"good things just happen"},{"time":343315,"text":"and the cynical who believe\nthat bad things just happen,"},{"time":346665,"text":"the fortunate and unfortunate alike"},{"time":349017,"text":"who think that their lot is simply what they deserve"},{"time":352540,"text":"rather than the eminently alterable result"},{"time":356501,"text":"of a prior arrangement, an inherited allocation,"},{"time":359783,"text":"of power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363446,"text":"As a result of all of this\ncreeping fatalism in public life,"},{"time":367122,"text":"we here, particularly in America today,"},{"time":369259,"text":"have depressingly low levels"},{"time":371141,"text":"of civic knowledge, civic engagement, participation,"},{"time":374199,"text":"awareness."},{"time":377380,"text":"The whole business of politics has been"},{"time":379258,"text":"effectively subcontracted out\nto a band of professionals,"},{"time":382950,"text":"money people, outreach people,"},{"time":384761,"text":"message people, research people."},{"time":386851,"text":"The rest of us are meant to feel like amateurs"},{"time":389922,"text":"in the sense of suckers."},{"time":392088,"text":"We become demotivated to learn more"},{"time":394614,"text":"about how things work."},{"time":395996,"text":"We begin to opt out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401590,"text":"Well, this problem, this challenge,"},{"time":405221,"text":"is a thing that we must now confront,"},{"time":407910,"text":"and I believe that when you have"},{"time":408901,"text":"this kind of disengagement, this willful ignorance,"},{"time":411880,"text":"it becomes both a cause and a consequence"},{"time":415359,"text":"of this concentration of opportunity"},{"time":418235,"text":"of wealth and clout that I was\ndescribing a moment ago,"},{"time":420596,"text":"this profound civic inequality."},{"time":424334,"text":"This is why it is so important in our time right now"},{"time":427475,"text":"to reimagine civics as the teaching of power."},{"time":430922,"text":"Perhaps it's never been more important"},{"time":433566,"text":"at any time in our lifetimes."},{"time":438955,"text":"If people don't learn power,"},{"time":440890,"text":"people don't wake up,"},{"time":442458,"text":"and if they don't wake up,"},{"time":444213,"text":"they get left out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446980,"text":"Now, part of the art of practicing power"},{"time":451452,"text":"means being awake and having a voice,"},{"time":453512,"text":"but it also is about having an arena"},{"time":455897,"text":"where you can plausibly practice deciding."},{"time":459959,"text":"All of civics boils down to the simple question"},{"time":462141,"text":"of who decides,"},{"time":463899,"text":"and you have to play that out"},{"time":465661,"text":"in a place, in an arena."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467694,"text":"And this brings me to the third\npoint that I want to make today,"},{"time":470622,"text":"which is simply that there is no better arena"},{"time":474233,"text":"in our time for the practicing of power"},{"time":477282,"text":"than the city."},{"time":480174,"text":"Think about the city where you live,"},{"time":482028,"text":"where you're from."},{"time":483885,"text":"Think about a problem in\nthe common life of your city."},{"time":487136,"text":"It can be something small,"},{"time":488169,"text":"like where a street lamp should go,"},{"time":490676,"text":"or something medium like"},{"time":492297,"text":"which library should have its hours extended or cut,"},{"time":496234,"text":"or maybe something bigger,"},{"time":497804,"text":"like whether a dilapidated waterfront should be"},{"time":500502,"text":"turned into a highway or a greenway,"},{"time":503437,"text":"or whether all the businesses in your town"},{"time":505135,"text":"should be required to pay a living wage."},{"time":509185,"text":"Think about the change that you want in your city,"},{"time":511536,"text":"and then think about how you would get it,"},{"time":515248,"text":"how you would make it happen."},{"time":518880,"text":"Take an inventory of all the forms of power"},{"time":521210,"text":"that are at play in your city's situation:"},{"time":524354,"text":"money, of course, people, yes,"},{"time":528693,"text":"ideas, information, misinformation,"},{"time":533603,"text":"the threat of force, the force of norms."},{"time":537227,"text":"All of these form of power are at play."},{"time":539138,"text":"Now think about how you would activate"},{"time":540680,"text":"or perhaps neutralize these various forms of power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545483,"text":"This is not some Game of Thrones"},{"time":548689,"text":"empire-level set of questions."},{"time":551025,"text":"These are questions that play out"},{"time":552918,"text":"in every single place on the planet."},{"time":555664,"text":"I'll just tell you quickly about two stories"},{"time":557823,"text":"drawn from recent headlines."},{"time":559859,"text":"In Boulder, Colorado,"},{"time":561301,"text":"voters not too long ago approved a process"},{"time":565290,"text":"to replace the private power company,"},{"time":568182,"text":"literally the power company,\nthe electric company Xcel,"},{"time":570494,"text":"with a publicly owned utility"},{"time":572790,"text":"that would forego profits"},{"time":574136,"text":"and attend far more to climate change."},{"time":577845,"text":"Well, Xcel fought back,"},{"time":579970,"text":"and Xcel has now put in play a ballot measure"},{"time":582330,"text":"that would undermine or undo"},{"time":584226,"text":"this municipalization."},{"time":586022,"text":"And so the citizen activists in\nBoulder who have been pushing this"},{"time":588636,"text":"now literally have to fight the power"},{"time":591370,"text":"in order to fight for power."},{"time":593969,"text":"In Tuscaloosa, at the University of Alabama,"},{"time":598342,"text":"there's an organization on campus"},{"time":600278,"text":"called, kind of menacingly, the Machine,"},{"time":604151,"text":"and it draws from largely white sororities"},{"time":607522,"text":"and fraternities on campus,"},{"time":608962,"text":"and for decades, the Machine has dominated"},{"time":611381,"text":"student government elections."},{"time":613234,"text":"Well now, recently, the Machine"},{"time":615630,"text":"has started to get involved"},{"time":616927,"text":"in actual city politics,"},{"time":618610,"text":"and they've engineered the election"},{"time":620268,"text":"of a former Machine member,"},{"time":621640,"text":"a young, pro-business recent graduate"},{"time":624346,"text":"to the Tuscaloosa city school board."},{"time":627860,"text":"Now, as I say, these are just two examples"},{"time":630696,"text":"drawn almost at random from the headlines."},{"time":633400,"text":"Every day, there are thousands more like them."},{"time":636600,"text":"And you may like or dislike"},{"time":638364,"text":"the efforts I'm describing here"},{"time":640269,"text":"in Boulder or in Tuscaloosa,"},{"time":641598,"text":"but you cannot help but admire"},{"time":644240,"text":"the power literacy of the players involved,"},{"time":647311,"text":"their skill."},{"time":648486,"text":"You cannot help but reckon with and recognize"},{"time":651462,"text":"the command they have"},{"time":653073,"text":"of the elemental questions"},{"time":655608,"text":"of civic power â€”"},{"time":657484,"text":"what objective, what strategy, what tactics,"},{"time":661522,"text":"what is the terrain, who are your enemies,"},{"time":664500,"text":"who are your allies?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666650,"text":"Now I want you to return"},{"time":668395,"text":"to thinking about that problem or that opportunity"},{"time":671790,"text":"or that challenge in your city,"},{"time":673951,"text":"and the thing it was that you want to fix"},{"time":675824,"text":"or create in your city,"},{"time":677635,"text":"and ask yourself,"},{"time":679950,"text":"do you have command of these\nelemental questions of power?"},{"time":683600,"text":"Could you put into practice effectively"},{"time":686650,"text":"what it is that you know?"},{"time":689664,"text":"This is the challenge and the opportunity for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694061,"text":"We live in a time right now"},{"time":696577,"text":"where in spite of globalization"},{"time":699564,"text":"or perhaps because of globalization,"},{"time":701724,"text":"all citizenship is ever more resonantly,"},{"time":703760,"text":"powerfully local."},{"time":705540,"text":"Indeed, power in our time is flowing"},{"time":708248,"text":"ever faster to the city."},{"time":710610,"text":"Here in the United States, the national government"},{"time":712258,"text":"has tied itself up in partisan knots."},{"time":715259,"text":"Civic imagination and innovation and creativity"},{"time":718181,"text":"are emerging from local ecosystems now"},{"time":720798,"text":"and radiating outward,"},{"time":722688,"text":"and this great innovation,"},{"time":726128,"text":"this great wave"},{"time":729055,"text":"of localism that's now arriving,"},{"time":732981,"text":"and you see it in how people eat"},{"time":734646,"text":"and work and share and buy and move"},{"time":737294,"text":"and live their everyday lives,"},{"time":738989,"text":"this isn't some precious parochialism,"},{"time":742142,"text":"this isn't some retreat into insularity, no."},{"time":745456,"text":"This is emergent."},{"time":747819,"text":"The localism of our time is networked powerfully."},{"time":751610,"text":"And so, for instance,"},{"time":752873,"text":"consider the ways that strategies"},{"time":755036,"text":"for making cities more bike-friendly"},{"time":757470,"text":"have spread so rapidly from Copenhagen"},{"time":760016,"text":"to New York to Austin to Boston to Seattle."},{"time":765138,"text":"Think about how experiments\nin participatory budgeting,"},{"time":768702,"text":"where everyday citizens get a chance"},{"time":770175,"text":"to allocate and decide upon"},{"time":772976,"text":"the allocation of city funds."},{"time":775910,"text":"Those experiments have\nspread from Porto Alegre, Brazil"},{"time":779490,"text":"to here in New York City, \nto the wards of Chicago."},{"time":783853,"text":"Migrant workers from Rome to Los Angeles"},{"time":785991,"text":"and many cities between"},{"time":788341,"text":"are now organizing to stage strikes"},{"time":790624,"text":"to remind the people who live in their cities"},{"time":792694,"text":"what a day without immigrants would look like."},{"time":795980,"text":"In China, all across that country,"},{"time":798438,"text":"members of the New Citizens' Movement"},{"time":800646,"text":"are beginning to activate and organize"},{"time":802232,"text":"to fight official corruption and graft,"},{"time":804886,"text":"and they're drawing the ire of officials there,"},{"time":806990,"text":"but they're also drawing the attention"},{"time":808733,"text":"of anti-corruption activists all around the world."},{"time":812288,"text":"In Seattle, where I'm from,"},{"time":814223,"text":"we've become part of a great global array of cities"},{"time":816669,"text":"that are now working together"},{"time":818228,"text":"bypassing government altogether,"},{"time":819758,"text":"national government altogether,"},{"time":822138,"text":"in order to try to meet the carbon reduction goals"},{"time":824487,"text":"of the Kyoto Protocol."},{"time":826627,"text":"All of these citizens, united,"},{"time":829670,"text":"are forming a web,"},{"time":831345,"text":"a great archipelago of power"},{"time":833358,"text":"that allows us to bypass"},{"time":835765,"text":"brokenness and monopolies of control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839669,"text":"And our task now is to accelerate this work."},{"time":842550,"text":"Our task now is to bring more and more people"},{"time":844664,"text":"into the fold of this work."},{"time":846695,"text":"That's why my organization, Citizen University,"},{"time":849444,"text":"has undertaken a project now"},{"time":851448,"text":"to create an everyman's curriculum"},{"time":854293,"text":"in civic power."},{"time":856610,"text":"And this curriculum starts with this triad"},{"time":858815,"text":"that I described earlier of values,"},{"time":860830,"text":"systems and skills."},{"time":863956,"text":"And what I'd like to do is to invite all of you"},{"time":866808,"text":"to help create this curriculum"},{"time":869458,"text":"with the stories and the experiences"},{"time":871885,"text":"and the challenges that each of you lives and faces,"},{"time":875142,"text":"to create something powerfully collective."},{"time":878146,"text":"And I want to invite you in particular to try"},{"time":880557,"text":"a simple exercise drawn"},{"time":882656,"text":"from the early frameworks of this curriculum."},{"time":885199,"text":"I want you to write a narrative,"},{"time":887630,"text":"a narrative from the future of your city,"},{"time":890680,"text":"and you can date it, set it out one year from now,"},{"time":894221,"text":"five years from now, a decade from now,"},{"time":895965,"text":"a generation from now,"},{"time":897766,"text":"and write it as a case study looking back,"},{"time":901611,"text":"looking back at the change"},{"time":903256,"text":"that you wanted in your city,"},{"time":905352,"text":"looking back at the cause\nthat you were championing,"},{"time":908091,"text":"and describing the ways that that change"},{"time":910825,"text":"and that cause came, in fact, to succeed."},{"time":915036,"text":"Describe the values"},{"time":916948,"text":"of your fellow citizens that you activated,"},{"time":919333,"text":"and the sense of moral purpose\nthat you were able to stir."},{"time":922940,"text":"Recount all the different ways"},{"time":924602,"text":"that you engaged the systems of government,"},{"time":927230,"text":"of the marketplace,"},{"time":928741,"text":"of social institutions, of faith organizations,"},{"time":930946,"text":"of the media."},{"time":934148,"text":"Catalog all the skills you had to deploy,"},{"time":938113,"text":"how to negotiate, how to advocate,"},{"time":940527,"text":"how to frame issues,"},{"time":941922,"text":"how to navigate diversity in conflict,"},{"time":944463,"text":"all those skills that enabled you"},{"time":946282,"text":"to bring folks on board"},{"time":948353,"text":"and to overcome resistance."},{"time":951050,"text":"What you'll be doing when you write that narrative"},{"time":954422,"text":"is you'll be discovering how to read power,"},{"time":958501,"text":"and in the process, how to write power."},{"time":963698,"text":"So share what you write,"},{"time":965903,"text":"do you what you write,"},{"time":967241,"text":"and then share what you do."},{"time":971058,"text":"I invite you to literally share"},{"time":973052,"text":"the narratives that you create"},{"time":974946,"text":"on our Facebook page for Citizen University."},{"time":977890,"text":"But even beyond that, it's in the conversations"},{"time":980572,"text":"that we have today"},{"time":982128,"text":"all around the world in the simultaneous gatherings"},{"time":984389,"text":"that are happening on this topic at this moment,"},{"time":987239,"text":"and to think about how we can become"},{"time":988990,"text":"one another's teachers and students in power."},{"time":992590,"text":"If we do that, then together"},{"time":994863,"text":"we can make civics sexy again."},{"time":997276,"text":"Together, we can democratize democracy"},{"time":999678,"text":"and make it safe again for amateurs."},{"time":1002888,"text":"Together, we can create a great network of city"},{"time":1007237,"text":"that will be the most powerful collective laboratory"},{"time":1009769,"text":"for self-government this planet has ever seen."},{"time":1013235,"text":"We have the power to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1016221,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018690,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}